t%20the%20British%20regime%20perpetuated%20itself%20by%20employing%20the%20doctrine%20of%20frightfulness.%C2%A0%20It%20struck%20fear%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20people%20who%C2%A0were%20expected%20to%20meekly%20surrender%20before%20the%20colonial%20authorities%20by%20accepting%20falsehoods%20spun%20by%20them%20and%20forsaking%20not%20just%20protest%20but%20even%20a%20questioning%20attitude%20either%20in%20public%20or%20through%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20doctrine%20of%20frightfulness%20is%20being%20replayed%20in%20the%20India%20of%202024.%20Those%20sections%20of%20the%20media%20which%20question%20the%20Modi%20regime%20are%20under%20attack%20and%20opposition%20parties%20are%20being%20split.%20People%E2%80%99s%20representatives%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20occupy%20high%20constitutional%20positions%2C%20are%20not%20spared.%20Many%20of%20them%20face%20jail%2C%20the%20threat%20of%20incarceration%20or%20repeated%20coercive%20action%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJail%20or%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2012%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20and%20a%20veteran%20leader%20of%20%C2%A0Congress%20resigned%20from%20the%20party.%20He%20was%20facing%20several%20corruption%20cases.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20The%20political%20buzz%20is%20that%20he%20was%20told%20he%20had%20two%20options%20%E2%80%93%20join%20the%20BJP%20or%20go%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20exemplifies%20how%20the%20doctrine%20of%20fear%20is%20used%20to%20actuate%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20a%20major%20state%20like%20Maharashtra%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20party%20and%20embrace%20the%20BJP.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20%C2%A0opposition%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20%C2%A0Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20were%20split%20as%20the%20doctrine%20of%20fear%20was%20invoked%20against%20key%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargeting%20media%20With%20doctrine%20of%20frightfulness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20newspapers%20and%20independent%20media%20platforms%20such%20as%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%C2%A0The%20Wire%20and%20Newslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0have%20faced%20punitive%20action.%C2%A0In%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20press%20club%20was%20shut%20down%20and%20several%20journalists%20were%20jailed%20on%20trumped%20up%20charges.%20In%20the%20case%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20its%20founding%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20faces%20terrorism%20charges%20under%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20law%20for%20%C2%A0discharging%20journalistic%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20often%20takes%20pride%20in%20saying%20that%20India%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20and%20yet%20his%20regime%20is%20acting%20contrary%20to%20basic%20democratic%20values.%20The%20relentless%20penal%20measures%20directed%20against%20the%20media%20flow%20from%20the%20doctrine%20of%20frightfulness%20which%20is%20applied%20with%20impunity%20to%20make%20independent%20and%20critical%20media%20subservient%20to%20the%20government%2C%20just%20as%20corporate%20media%20already%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20remind%20us%20of%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20martial%20law%20imposed%20in%20Punjab%20following%20the%20Jallianwala%20Bagh%20%C2%A0massacre%20and%20the%20suppression%20of%20the%20press.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20in%20his%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fee01389b-a997-4247-ab9b-cc72b0069edb%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fee01389b-a997-4247-ab9b-cc72b0069edb%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708081370779000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3yFvEX-FOOOFNgthCWnWHk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20on%20the%20Punjab%20Disorders%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0observed%20that%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20existence%20of%20independent%20journalism%20became%20an%20impossibility%20during%20the%20Martial%20Law%20regime%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPunjabee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPratap%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0stopped%20publishing%E2%80%9D.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThose%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20resonate%20in%20India%20now%20when%20there%20is%20a%20great%20threat%20posed%20to%20independent%20journalism%20and%20those%20media%20platforms%20who%20dare%20to%20question%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20prophetic%20observations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20after%20drafting%C2%A0%E2%80%9CPunjab%20Disorder%E2%80%9D%20his%20Punjab%20report%2C%20%C2%A0Gandhi%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20delivered%20on%2023rd%20August%201920%20at%20Bezwada%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20British%20Government%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6does%20not%20scruple%20to%20use%20means%20fair%20or%20foul%20in%20order%20to%20gain%20its%20ends%E2%80%9D.%20As%20the%20massive%20crowd%20attentively%20listening%20to%20him%20cried%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CShame!%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarked%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CNo%20craft%20is%20above%20that%20Government%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20forcefully%20added%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIt%20resorts%20to%20frightfulness%2C%20terrorism.%20It%20resorts%20to%20bribery%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20titles%2C%20honours%20and%20high%20offices%E2%80%9D.%20The%20crowd%20again%20cried%2C%20%E2%80%9CShame!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20possibly%20would%20have%20used%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfrightfulness%2C%20terrorism%2C%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0if%20he%20had%20been%20alive%20in%20the%20India%20of%202024.%20He%20charged%20that%20titles%2C%20honours%20and%20high%20offices%20offered%20by%20the%20British%20rulers%20amounted%20to%20%C2%A0bribery.%20In%20retrospect%20those%20words%20assume%20relevance%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20recent%20announcement%20of%20%C2%A0Bharat%20Ratnas%20for%20personalities%20such%20as%20Karpoori%20%C2%A0Thakur%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20and%20M.S.%20Swaminathan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20speech%2C%20Gandhi%20very%20critically%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20administers%20opiates%20in%20the%20form%20of%20reforms%E2%80%A6%20In%20any%20sense%20it%20is%20autocracy%20doubly%20distilled%2C%20appearing%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20democracy%20for%20the%20greatest%20gifts%20of%20a%20crafty%2C%20cunning%20man%20are%20worthless%20so%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Elong%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0as%20cunning%20resides%20in%20his%20heart%E2%80%9D.%20Very%20prescient%20articulations%20indeed!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20also%20clear%20about%20the%20message%20he%20had%20for%20the%20people.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20have%20given%20to%20you%20these%20qualities%20of%20this%20Government%20not%20in%20order%20to%20excite%20your%20angry%20passions%20but%20in%20order%20that%20you%20may%20appreciate%20fully%20the%20forces%20that%20are%20matched%20against%20you%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAnger%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20serve%20no%20purpose.%E2%80%9D%20He%20then%20firmly%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9C%20We%20shall%20have%20to%20meet%20their%20untruth%20by%20truth.%20We%20shall%20have%20to%20meet%20terrorism%2C%20their%20frightfulness%20by%20bravery%2C%20and%20it%20is%20an%20unbending%20bravery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20now%20a%C2%A0replay%20of%20the%20doctrine%20of%20frightfulness%20and%20it%20is%20amply%20manifested%20in%20India.%20The%20assertion%20of%20Gandhi%20that%20truth%20has%20to%20be%20employed%20to%20counter%20untruth%20and%20terrorism%20and%20frightfulness%20by%20bravery%20and%2C%20that%20too%20unbending%20bravery%2C%20is%20surely%20a%20manifesto%20for%20our%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R