0process%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20creativity%20is%20kind%20of%20bogged%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20to%20succeed%20came%20early.%20Capri%20started%20her%20YouTube%20channel%20in%202018%20and%20hit%20a%20million%20subscribers%20within%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20it%20as%20the%20opportunity%20of%20a%20lifetime%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flizzy-capri-quit-day-job-for-youtube-got-millions-subcribers-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20quit%20her%20job%20at%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20making%20content%20packed%20full%20of%20ball%20pits%2C%20fidget%20spinners%2C%20and%20unboxing%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20became%20a%20firm%20favorite%20star%20among%20children%2C%20who%20loved%20her%20vibrant%2C%20candy-colored%20videos%20about%20slime%2C%20pranks%2C%20and%20all%20things%20pink%2C%20and%20earned%20more%20than%20seven%20million%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20on%20the%20outside%20there%20was%20only%20success%2C%20on%20the%20inside%2C%20Capri%20was%20burning%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20felt%20less%20and%20less%20connected%20to%20her%20fan%20base%20and%20started%20thinking%20her%20channel%2C%20with%20its%20vivid%20colors%20and%20exaggerated%20video%20thumbnails%20and%20titles%2C%20wasn't%20representative%20of%20who%20she%20was%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20brain%20has%20been%20so%20trained%20over%20the%20past%20six%2C%20seven%20years%20to%20just%20make%20super%20colorful%2C%20crazy%20thumbnails%20that%20are%20a%20spectacle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20I'm%20just%20like%2C%20I%20can't%20sit%20here%20and%20watch%20my%20own%20videos%20because%20they're%20not%20fun%20for%20me%20to%20watch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222882%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lizzy%20Capri%20YouTube%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ccb52694aa8ee8e84b2734%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221588%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELizzy%20Capri%20grew%20a%20strong%20fanbase%20with%20her%20candy-colored%20thumbnails%20and%20exaggerated%20content.%3Cp%3ELizzy%20Capri%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20isolating%20having%20this%20character%20be%20so%20intertwined%20with%20her%20real%20life%2C%20she%20said%2C%20where%20everything%20in%20her%20life%20was%20bubblegum%20pink%2C%20including%20her%20car%20and%20her%20entire%20house%2C%20down%20to%20her%20bedsheets%20and%20towels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20actually%20a%20study%20that%20if%20you%20stay%20in%20a%20room%20that's%20all%20pink%2C%20at%20first%20it%20seems%20nice%2C%20but%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20it%20makes%20you%20go%20insane.%20And%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20happened%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapri%20says%20she%20sees%20her%20journey%20a%20little%20like%20Miley%20Cyrus's%2C%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20out%20of%20that%20kid's%20realm%20and%20into%20her%20own%20self.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20she%20started%20an%20OnlyFans.%20The%20venture%20venture%20seems%20to%20be%20paying%20off%2C%20though%2C%20having%20earned%20around%20%24100%2C000%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20sent%20over%20by%20her%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20chose%20OnlyFans%20because%20of%20the%20stigma%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapri%20said%20she%20has%20always%20been%20insecure%20about%20her%20body%20and%20her%20appearance%2C%20and%20OnlyFans%20helped%20boost%20her%20confidence.%20Her%20account%20is%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20for%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20there%20is%20no%20full-on%20nudity%20on%20there%2C%20and%20she%20sees%20it%20more%20as%20%26quot%3Bartistic%20expression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20keeps%20me%20motivated%20to%20stick%20to%20my%20workout%20routines%20because%20when%20I%20look%20good%2C%20I%20feel%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20