political%20storm%20over%20BJP's%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20allowed%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20party%20of%20inciting%20trouble%20on%20the%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20allowed%20injustice%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20sent%20(representatives%20of)%20the%20state%20women's%20commission%20(to%20Sandeshkhali)%20immediately%20and%2017%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20shortly%20after%20main%20Opposition%20BJP%20staged%20a%20walkout%20over%20the%20raging%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlaming%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20unrest%20on%20the%20island%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20said%20the%20Centre%20had%20targeted%20local%20Trinamool%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20through%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20they%20entered%20the%20area%20and%20targeted%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20though%20ED%20and%20then%20they%20started%20the%20trouble%20there%20by%20getting%20people%20in.%20There%20is%20an%20RSS%20base%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20There%20were%20riots%20earlier%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%2C%20a%20local%20strongman%2C%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20for%20a%20month%20now%20after%20ED%20officials%20who%20visited%20the%20island%20to%20raid%20his%20home%20came%20under%20a%20mob%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20said%20a%20police%20team%20is%20meeting%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20%26quot%3BA%20police%20team%20of%20women%20are%20going%20door%20to%20door%20to%20see%20if%20there%20are%20any%20complaints.%20If%20they%20file%20a%20report%2C%20we%20will%20look%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeshkhali%20has%20hit%20headlines%20after%20the%20BJP%20accused%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20The%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20allegations.%20The%20ruling%20party%20has%20trashed%20the%20charges%20and%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20unrest%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20island%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20an%20uneasy%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20visited%20Sandeshkhali%20yesterday%20and%20spoke%20to%20several%20women.%20The%20conversations%20revealed%20that%20while%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20of%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%20may%20not%20be%20true%2C%20many%20women%20were%20called%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20office%20at%20odd%20hours%20and%20threatened%20if%20they%20refused.%20Some%20women%20also%20said%20that%20their%20husbands%20were%20being%20tortured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20protests%20earlier%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20incidents%20must%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20otherwise%20why%20will%20the%20women%20say%20these%20things%3F%20You%20must%20enquire%20for%20yourself.%20Why%20else%20will%20women%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20speak%20out%3F%20Are%20they%20lying%3F%20There%20must%20be%20truth%20in%20these%20statements.%C2%A0We%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20We%20don't%20come%20out%20of%20our%20homes%20because%20of%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(Shahjahan's%20aides)%20would%20call%20women%20for%20meetings%20or%20rallies%20but%20there%20was%20no%20fixed%20time.%20It%20could%20be%20day%20or%20night.%20We%20would%20have%20to%20go%20whenever%20they%20called%20us%20and%20if%20we%20didn't%2C%20they%20would%20threaten%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20named%20Shahjahan's%20aides%2C%20Shibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%20While%20Sardar%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20Hazra%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20women%20alleged%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20leaders%20would%20torture%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20targeted%20women%20by%20picking%20up%20their%20husbands%20and%20beating%20them%20up%20with%20a%20stick%20in%20the%20party%20office.%20If%20we%20refused%20to%20go%20to%20the%20party%20office%2C%20they%20would%20pick%20up%20the%20men%20and%20thrash%20them%20so%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20have%20said%20a%20section%20of%20media%20is%20spreading%20%26quot%3Bwilful%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20to%20mislead%20people%20about%20the%20events%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20reiterated%20that%20no%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20torture%20of%20women%20have%20so%20far%20been%20received%20during%20the%20enquiries%20since%20conducted%20by%20the%20State%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20an%20all-women%2010-member%20fact-finding%20team%20led%20by%20DIG%20CID%2C%20and%20also%20the%20district%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708001820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F1q9e5as_sandeshkhali_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandeshkhali-row-5062193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20political%20storm%20over%20BJP's%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20allowed%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20inciting%20trouble%20on%20the%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandeshkhali-row-5062193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandes