-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eimproving%20heart%20health%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsedentary-lifestyle-associated-with-increased-risk-of-cancer-study-finds-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20the%20risk%20of%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20Greger%20works%20from%20home%2C%20he%20walks%20all%20day%20on%20a%20treadmill%20desk%20set%20to%20two%20to%20three%20miles%20per%20hour.%20He%20estimated%20that%20he%20walks%20around%2014%20miles%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20keeps%20me%20from%20being%20sedentary%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20really%20give%20me%20exercise%20per%20se%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGet%20his%20heart%20rate%20up%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGreger%20makes%20sure%20that%20he%20gets%20his%20heart%20rate%20up%20every%20day%20in%20some%20way%2C%20aiming%20to%20do%2090%20minutes%20of%20moderate%20or%2040%20minutes%20of%20vigorous%20exercise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20on%20the%20road%20for%20a%20speaking%20tour%20when%20he%20spoke%20to%20BI%20and%20is%20the%20first%20to%20admit%20that%20maintaining%20healthy%20habits%20can%20be%20tough%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20traveling.%20So%20he%20works%20with%20what%20he%20has%20available.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20new%20apartment%20I%20have%20by%20the%20airport%20is%20on%20the%2018th%20floor%2C%20so%20I%20try%20to%20jog%20up%2018%20floors%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20packs%20a%20resistance%20band%20and%20does%20burpees%20if%20the%20place%20where%20he%E2%80%99s%20staying%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20stairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEat%20calories%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20earlier%20rather%20than%20later%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20beneficial%20for%20health%20and%20longevity%20because%20of%20how%20our%20circadian%20rhythm%20works%2C%20Greger%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3