0said%20the%20staff%20member%20looked%20at%20the%20slip%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20that%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStewart%20said%20she%20asked%20what%20she%20should%20be%20tipping%2C%20and%20the%20woman%20recommended%20%2420-%2430.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20then%20wanted%20to%20stick%20up%20for%20herself%20because%20she%20found%20the%20interaction%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20rude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20the%20receptionist%20she%20wouldn't%20be%20tipping%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20goes%2C%20well%2C%20the%20girls%20here%20work%20really%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Stewart%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20said%2C%20oh%2C%20I'm%20not%20questioning%20that%20at%20all.%20I'm%20sure%20they%20do%2C%20but%20that's%20why%20I%20am%20already%20paying%20%2480.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20receptionist%20then%20told%20her%20that%20the%20amount%20just%20covered%20the%20salon's%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I'm%20like%2C%20well%2C%20respectfully%2C%20that's%20not%20my%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Stewart%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sorry%20if%20maybe%20your%20boss%20doesn't%20pay%20you%20guys%20enough.%20That's%20really%20unfortunate%2C%20but%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20up%20to%20me%20to%20make%20up%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStewart%20said%20she%20then%20went%20into%20the%20room%20for%20the%20massage%20but%20she%20heard%20the%20receptionist%20speaking%20with%20her%20masseuse%20outside.%20They%20weren't%20speaking%20English%2C%20she%20said%2C%20but%20she%20had%20a%20feeling%20they%20were%20talking%20about%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20a%20bad%20vibe%2C%20bad%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I'm%20like%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20leave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStewart%20said%20she%20gathered%20her%20belongings%20and%20started%20to%20leave%20the%20salon%2C%20deciding%20she%20would%20just%20get%20a%20refund%20from%20her%20credit%20card%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20receptionist%20then%20chased%20her%20out%20the%20door%2C%20asking%20her%20to%20come%20back.%20She%20even%20offered%20a%20discount%2C%20Stewart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20well%2C%20no%2C%20that's%20fine.%20I'm%20fine%20with%20paying%20full%20price.%20I'm%20fine%20with%20leaving%20the%20tip.%20I'm%20not%20trying%20to%20pay%20less%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20happy%20with%20paying%20the%20full%20price%20and%20the%20tip%2C%20but%20I%20just%20don't%20appreciate%20being%20made%20to%20feel%20bad%20for%20what%20I%20am%20able%20to%20tip%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStewart%20said%20the%20receptionist%20then%20assured%20her%20they%20weren't%20talking%20about%20her%2C%20which%20she%20found%20strange.%20But%20she%20decided%20to%20go%20through%20with%20the%20massage%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20masseuse%20did%20a%20good%20job%2C%20and%20so%20she%20added%20another%20%245%20to%20her%20tip%2C%20totaling%20%2410.%20But%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20whole%20time%20she%20was%20lying%20there%2C%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Boverthinking%26quot%3B%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20changed%20the%20tip%20to%2010.%20Everything%20was%20good.%20Told%20them%20to%20have%20a%20good%20night.%20Everything%20was%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20left%20still%20just%20thinking%20to%20myself%2C%20was%20that%20kind%20of%20rude%20or%20am%20I%20a%20cheap%20person%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20expressed%20their%20discomfort%20with%20Stewart's%20experience%20in%20the%20comments%2C%20saying%20tipping%20before%20a%20service%20was%20%26quot%3Bcrazy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20from%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F1094670519900553%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Service%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20found%20that%20customers%20really%20dislike%20tipping%20before%20they're%20served%2C