in%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15154000%2FIMG_4185-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENabin%20Das%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%202019%20and%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20elections%20in%202021%20%E2%80%93%20like%20most%20others%20in%20his%20Matua%20community%20%E2%80%93%20and%20switched%20to%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%202023.%20He%20waited%20for%20five%20years%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20implement%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20hoping%20it%20would%20clarify%20his%20citizenship%20status.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20do%20not%20have%20card%20issued%20by%20the%20government%2C%20would%20that%20mean%20we%20would%20lose%20various%20allowances%20that%20we%20receive%20from%20the%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Das%2C%20a%20transport%20worker%20from%20Gaighata%2C%20on%20the%20Bangladesh-India%20border%2C%20near%20Bangaon%C2%A0in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20in%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bangaon%2C%20Mitali%20Biswas%2C%20a%20homemaker%20belonging%20to%20the%20same%20sect%2C%20has%20a%20very%20different%20take%20on%20the%20issue.%20A%20beneficiary%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%E2%80%99s%20Lakshmir%20Bhandar%20incentive%20programme%2C%20she%20receives%20Rs%2010%2C00%20per%20month%20while%20her%20two%20daughters%20get%20Rs%201%2C000%20each%20per%20year%20from%20the%20state-run%20Kanyashree%20scheme.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrateful%20for%20the%20government%20support%2C%20Biswas%20makes%20her%20priorities%20quite%20clear%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20would%20happen%20with%20these%20cards%20and%20new%20regulations%3F%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20when%20we%20came%20to%20this%20country%2C%20we%20vote.%20All%20our%20records%20like%20ration%20cards%2C%20voter%20ID%20and%20Aadhaar%20are%20ready%20with%20us.%20This%20is%20intimidation%20tactics%20for%20political%20gain!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAA%20and%20NRC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20elections%20looming%2C%20the%20CAA%20is%20again%20being%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20junior%20union%20ports%20and%20shipping%20minister%20Santanu%20Thakur%20had%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshantanu-thakur-matua-caa-bjp-bengal%5C%22%3E%20retract%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20statement%20on%20CAA%20which%20he%20claimed%20would%20be%20implemented%20%E2%80%9Cwithin%20a%20week%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20on%20January%2028.%20Reportedly%2C%20he%20was%20admonished%20internally%20by%20the%20party%20following%20an%20outcry%20against%20CAA%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%20forming%20the%20second%20largest%20scheduled%20caste%20group%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20comprising%203.8%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20the%20Matuas%20have%20demanded%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20for%20years%20now%20and%20form%20one%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20support%20bases%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20uncertainty%20over%20CAA%20has%20caused%20a%20feeling%20of%20disappointment%20and%20frustration%20among%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20community%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Nadia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20refuse%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20diktats%20of%20any%20political%20party%20or%20leader%2C%20they%20threaten%20to%20tag%20me%20as%20an%20illegal%20settler%20from%20Bangladesh.%20Government%20officials%20arrive%20for%20inspections%2C%20demanding%20land%20documents%2C%20residency%20proof%20and%20various%20other%20certificates.%20We%20need%20to%20settle%20this%20through%20bribery.%20Perhaps%20a%20card%20could%20ease%20this%20harassment!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shyamali%20Sardar%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fear%20that%20poor%20women%20are%20experiencing%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20propaganda.%20This%20is%20because%20individuals%20receiving%20rice%20obtain%20government%20funds%20via%20their%20bank%20accounts.%20Opening%20a%20bank%20account%20requires%20essential%20documentation%20from%20citizens%2C%20so%20the%20fear%20of%20discontinuing%20government%20aid%20is%20unfounded%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20economist%20Prasenjit%20Bose%2C%20who%20for%20years%20has%20been%20campaigning%20among%20the%20Matuas%20on%20the%20fallacy%20of%20CAA.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20actuality%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20introduce%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20in%20the%20future%2C%20and%20the%20current%20measures%20or%20examinations%20are%20integral%20to%20that%20strategy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindu%20identity%20and%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20identity%20card%E2%80%99%20is%20once%20again%20being%20wielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20win%20back%20Matua%20vote%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20which%20shifted%20to%20Trinamool%20Congress%20during%20the%202023%20Panchayat%20elections.%20Santanu%20Thakur%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20most%20prominent%20face%20and%20a%20descendant%20of%20Matua%20Mahasangha%20founder%20Harichand%20Thakur%2C%20asserts%20that%20they%20have%20issued%20a%20religion-specific%20identity%20document%20to%20Matua%20followers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20the%20NRC%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20solely%20about%20the%20CAA.%20The%20Matua%20Mahasangha%20has%20been%20issuing%20an%20identity%20card%20mentioning%20the%20religion%20of%20Matuas%20from%20the%20Matua%20Mahasangha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20help%20the%20government%20scrutinise%20quickly%20and%20avoid%20inconvenience%20during%20the%20CAA%20implementation.%20Providing%20shelter%20to%20refugees%20is%20our%20duty%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15153426%2F426400600_449638787387958_6463707409929905467_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15153426%2F426400600_449638787387958_6463707409929905467_n.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15153426%2F426400600_449638787387958_6463707409929905467_n-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15153426%2F426400600_449638787387958_6463707409929905467_n-1024x679.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20with%20members%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Matua%20Mahasangha%2C%20which%20he%20heads.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FAll%20India%20Matua%20Mahasangha%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20Bongaon%2C%20Thakurnagar%2C%20Gaighata%2C%20or%20Ranaghat%2C%20there%20are%20few%20takers%20for%20the%20card%E2%80%93issued%20by%20both%20factions%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%94headed%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20and%20his%20aunt%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Mamatabala%20Thakur.%20Even%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Haringhata%20in%20Nadia%20district%2C%20Asim%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20Matua%20community%20himself%2C%20has%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cbogus.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-why-the-bjp-brings-up-the-caa-but-stops-short-of-implementing-it-in-bengal%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20Why%20the%20BJP%20Brings%20up%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Stops%20Short%20of%20Implementing%20it%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrikanta%20Biswas%2C%20while%20agreeing%20with%20Sarkar%E2%80%99s%20viewpoint%2C%20sees%20the%20card%20as%20a%20form%20of%20insurance%20against%20potential%20harassment%20at%20his%20workplace%20in%20North%20India.%20A%20migrant%20worker%20from%20Gaighata%2C%20he%20always%20carries%20the%20card%20along%20with%20other%20government-issued%20identity%20proofs.%20He%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20religion%20is%20mentioned%20on%20the%20card.%20When%20police%20question%20us%2C%20suspecting%20us%20as%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%2C%20we%20show%20them%20the%20card%20which%20indicates%20we%E2%80%99re%20Hindus.%20This%20provides%20us%20with%20additional%20security.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Infiltrators%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMatuas%2C%20predominantly%20belonging%20to%20the%20Namashudra%20community%2C%20migrated%20from%20East%20Pakistan%20and%20later%20Bangladesh%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution%20and%20communal%20tension.%20The%20Matua%20Mahasangha%20gained%20prominence%20after%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20of%202003%20when%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20in%20coalition%20with%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20Centre.%20Since%20then%20Matua%20refugees%20have%20regularly%20faced%20suspicion%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98Bangladeshis%E2%80%99%20or%20illegal%20infiltrators%20during%20registration%20for%20electoral%20rolls%20and%20issuance%20of%20documents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20country%20free%20from%20infiltrators.%20We%20expect%20CAA%20to%20be%20implemented%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20declares%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20using%20refugee-infiltrator%20distinction%20to%20bring%20the%20lower%20caste%20Namashudra%20vote%20to%20their%20side%20by%20treating%20them%20as%20persecuted%20Hindu%20refugees%2C%20while%20projecting%20Muslims%20as%20encroachers%20from%20outside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20at%20least%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Nadia%20where%20the%20Matuas%20hold%20influence.%20In%20two%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20Bangaon%20and%20Ranaghat%2C%20the%20Matuas%20constitute%20over%2040%25%20of%20the%20electorate.%20The%20BJP%20won%20both%20the%20seats%20in%202019%20and%2014%20of%20the%2015%20assembly%20seats%20in%202021%20in%20the%20Matua%20belt%20of%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024%20Parganas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20success%20can%20be%20attributed%20largely%20to%20the%20suspicion%20and%20unease%20prevailing%20among%20substantial%20sections%20of%20the%20Hindu%20population%2C%20particularly%20the%20Matua%20community%2C%20over%20the%20minority%20population%20in%20the%20bordering%20districts%2C%20which%20the%20saffron%20camp%20labels%20as%20Bangladeshi%20Muslim%20infiltrators.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarrative%20building%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pro-Hindu%20narrative%20encoded%20in%20the%20CAA%20is%20aimed%20at%20consolidating%20the%20traditional%20Hindu%20vote%20bank%20of%20the%20BJP.%20There%20are%20two%20aspects%20of%20such%20calculations-one%20relate%20to%20the%20Namashudra-Matua%20community%20and%20the%20other%20pertains%20to%20the%20pro-Hindu%20messaging%20to%20the%20general%20Hindu%20population%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ayan%20Guha%2C%20British%20Academy%20International%20Fellow%2C%20School%20of%20Global%20Studies%2C%20University%20of%20Sussex%2C%20UK%20who%20has%20authored%20a%20book%20on%20caste%20politics%20in%20Bengal%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EThe%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20Politics%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithin%20the%20Matua%20community%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20concern%20about%20prioritising%20Hindutva%20over%20social%20reform.%20The%20Matua%20sect%20was%20founded%20by%20Harichand%20Thakur%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20on%20only%20three%20basic%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20truth%2C%20love%20and%20sanity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHarichand%20Thakur%E2%80%99s%20son%20Guruchand%20Thakur%2C%20one%20of%20the%20early%20reformers%20preaching%20abolition%20of%20caste%20inequality%2C%20and%20gender%20equality%20through%20secular%20duties%20went%20to%20Muslim-run%20%3Cem%3Emoktab%3C%2Fem%3E%20when%20he%20was%20denied%20education%20for%20his%20caste.%20This%20politics%20over%20CAA%20is%20shocking.%20It%E2%80%99s%20clear%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20centre%20is%20trying%20to%20fan%20Hindutva%20to%20polarise%20Hindu%20vote.%20But%20how%20can%20they%20overlook%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Matua%20movement%20against%20Manuvadi%20Brahminism%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Arun%20Mahapatra%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMatua%20Matadarsha%20Samajik%20Diker%20Koyekti%20Katha%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Some%20Words%20on%20the%20Social%20Direction%20of%20the%20Matua%20Thought%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20now%20become%20more%20of%20a%20family%20fight.%20The%20politicisation%20of%3Cem%3E%20thakur%20bari%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20split%20the%20Matua%20Mahasangha.%20The%20cherished%20principles%20of%20Harichand%20and%20Guruchand%20Thakur%20are%20now%20being%20compromised%20in%20favour%20of%20Hindutva.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20echoes%20local%20teacher%20Anupam%20Biswas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETMC%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20lost%20considerable%20support%20within%20the%20community%2C%20has%20been%20banking%20on%20this%20discord%20to%20sustain%20momentum%20following%20its%20success%20in%20the%202023%20Panchayat%20elections.%20The%20recent%20arrest%20of%20Jyotipriya%20Mallick%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20ration%20scam%2C%20however%2C%20has%20dealt%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20party.%20Since%202008%2C%20Mallick%20served%20as%20the%20bridge%20between%20%3Cem%3Ethakurbari%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Thakurnagar%20near%20Bangaon%2C%20preparations%20are%20underway%20for%20installation%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20Matua%20matriarch%20Binapani%20Devi%2C%20popular%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBoroma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%20There%20is%20a%20prevailing%20sense%20of%20uncertainty%20among%20the%20general%20public%20members%20over%20control%20of%20the%20organisation%20and%20CAA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20MP%20made%20false%20promises%20about%20granting%20citizenship.%20He%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20anything%20about%20it%20in%20five%20years.%20We%20want%20unconditional%20citizenship%2C%20or%20else%20we%20will%20start%20a%20hunger%20strike%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20believe%20that%20if%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20come%20to%20power%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20Matuas%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20former%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Thakur%20family%20Mamata%20Bala%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKapil%20Krishna%20Thakur%2C%20a%20local%20Matua%20face%20from%20the%20left%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20raise%20voice%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20of%202003.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMatua%20is%20not%20the%20problem%3B%20the%20obstacles%20posed%20by%20the%20citizenship%20law%20needs%20to%20be%20eliminated.%20In%202003%2C%20a%20new%20law%20was%20introduced%20defining%20illegal%20entry%2C%20and%20upon%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20agreement%2C%20the%20law%20was%20enacted.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20President%20again%20endorsed%20that%20law%20and%20ma