20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Election%20Commission%20data%2C%2028%2C030%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2016%2C437.63%20crore%20were%20sold%20between%202016%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20the%20primary%20beneficiary%20of%20these%20donations%20and%20received%20Rs%2010%2C122%20crore%2C%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations.%20The%20main%20opposition%20Congress%20party%20came%20a%20distant%20second%2C%20receiving%20Rs%201%2C547%20crore%20or%2010%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20while%20West%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20got%20Rs%20823%20crore%20or%208%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonations%20made%20to%20the%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20three%20times%20more%20than%20that%20of%20all%20other%2030%20parties%20combined%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20donations%20received%20by%20seven%20national%20parties%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%3A%20Rs%2010%2C122%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCongress%3A%20Rs%201%2C547%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnTMC%3A%20Rs%20823%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCPI(M)%3A%20Rs%20367%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnNCP%3A%20Rs%20231%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnBSP%3A%20Rs%2085%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCPI%3A%20Rs%2013%20crore%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEC%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20from%202017%20to%202022%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20over%20five%20times%20the%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20than%20the%20Congress%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20had%20been%20brought%20to%20curb%20black%20money%20and%20bring%20transparency%20into%20political%20donations%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinancial-support-to-political-parties-can-lead-to-quid-pro-quo-supreme-court-5061117%5C%22%3Eobjectives%20do%20not%20justify%20the%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ad