0'I%20Told%20You%20So'%20Moment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20unconstitutional%2C%20the%20CPM%2C%20also%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20case%2C%20welcomed%20the%20verdict%20and%20said%20details%20of%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20must%20come%20out.%20The%20CPM%20is%20the%20only%20major%20political%20party%20that%20did%20not%20accept%20donations%20by%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20had%20challenged%20the%20scheme%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20on%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20scheme%2C%20CPI(M)%20Secretary-General%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BCPM%20was%20the%20only%20petitioner%2C%20the%20only%20political%20party%20who%20had%20the%20locus-standi%20to%20argue%20against%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%2C%20we%20are%20the%20only%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJFzI3fzhzV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJFzI3fzhzV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1758040415289135122%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20this.%20We%20are%20a%20petitioner%2C%20the%20only%20political%20party%20that%20had%20the%20locus%20standi%20to%20argue%20against%20electoral%20bonds.%20We%20are%20the%20only%20party%20that%20did%20not%20express%20any%20electoral%20bond%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%20because%20we%20consider%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20as%20a%20legalisation%20of%20political%20corruption%20and%20this%20had%20to%20be%20ended%2C%26quot%3B%20CPM%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20leader%20also%20said%20the%20court%20has%20significantly%20ordered%20that%20details%20of%20donations%20made%20through%20this%20method%20be%20made%20public.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20element%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20This%20has%20clearly%20exposed%20this%20government's%20claims%20of%20fighting%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yechury%20also%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20that%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%20contribution%26quot%3B%20by%20companies%20to%20political%20parties%20is%20antithetical%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20amendment%20was%20moved%20in%20Parliament%2C%20I%20was%20a%20member.%20I%20remember%20we%20had%20a%20very%20heated%20argument%20with%20the%20then%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20late%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20that%20you%20are%20opening%20up%20the%20way%20for%20money%20laundering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%2C%20calling%20the%20judgment%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBy%20this%20verdict%2C%20this%20unscrupulous%20scheme%20designed%20to%20finance%20the%20ruling%20party%20by%20anonymous%20corporate%20donors%20has%20been%20completely%20scrapped%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20out%20with%20an%20official%20response%20to%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20unanimous%20judgment%2C%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrchud%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20this%20morning%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20violates%20the%20citizens'%20right%20to%20information.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20directed%20that%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20must%20stop%20issue%20of%20these%20bonds%20at%20once%20and%20provide%20details%20of%20donations%20made%20through%20this%20mode%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20The%20poll%20body%20was%20asked%20to%20publish%20this%20information%20on%20its%20website%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707987300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2F3d23c5vg_sitaram-yechury-pti_625x300_24_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sitaram-yechury-cpm-electoral-bonds-supreme-courts-electoral-bond-verdict-gives-cpm-a-i-told-you-so-moment-5062176%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20unconstitutional%2C%20the%20CPM%2C%20also%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20case%2C%20welcomed%20the%20verdict%20and%20said%20details%20of%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20must%20come%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sitaram-yechury-cpm-electoral-bonds-supreme-courts-electoral-bond-verdict-gives-cpm-a-i-told-you-so-moment-5062176%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sitaram-yechury-cpm-electoral-bonds-supreme-courts-electoral-bond-verdict-gives-cpm-a-i-told-you-so-moment-5062176%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sitaram-yechury-cpm-electoral-bonds-supreme-courts-electoral-bond-verdict-gives-cpm-a-i-told-you-so-moment-5062176%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IT%20Ministry%20Decides%20to%20Block%20Proton%20Mail%20After%20Fake%20Bomb%20Threats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15135644%2FProton-Mail-logo.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20IT%20ministry%20decided%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%20to%20block%20the%20Proton%20Mail%20email%20service%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fit-ministry-looks-to-block-proton-mail-on-request-of-tamil-nadu-police-101707938167006.html%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20ministry%20has%20not%20yet%20issued%20a%20final%20blocking%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20learnt%20that%20the%20ministry%20decided%20to%20block%20Proton%20Mail%20after%20a%20request%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%2C%20which%20said%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fchennai-citys-popular-schools-receive-bomb-threat-mail-police-after-checking-declare-it-a-hoax%2Farticle67826026.ece%5C%22%3Ea%20hoax%20bomb%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20sent%20to%2013%20schools%20in%20the%20Chennai%20area%20last%20week%20using%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nodal%20officer%20representing%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20said%20yesterday%20that%20attempts%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%E2%80%99%20IP%20addresses%20and%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20Interpol%20did%20not%20bear%20fruit%2C%20the%20newspaper%20also%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20officer%20was%20present%20at%20a%20committee%20meeting%20held%20as%20part%20of%20the%20online%20content%20blocking%20process%20relating%20to%20Section%2069A%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20the%20IT%20ministry%20noted%20during%20the%20meeting%20that%20receiving%20information%20from%20Proton%20Mail%20on%20criminal%20matters%20was%20a%20recurrent%20problem%2C%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProton%2C%20the%20Swiss%20software%20company%20that%20offers%20the%20Proton%20Mail%20service%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20IT%20ministry%20had%20notified%20it%20about%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpotential%20block%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20it%20was%20considering%20a%20way%20to%20work%20with%20Indian%20authorities%20in%20order%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN1ZS1L1%2F%5C%22%3ERussia%E2%80%99s%20government%20also%20decided%20to%20block%20Proton%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%2C%20saying%20Proton%20did%20not%20provide%20it%20with%20information%20on%20users%20who%20allegedly%20sent%20fake%20bomb%20threats%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20condemn%20this%20block%20as%20a%20misguided%20measure%20which%20only%20serves%20to%20harm%20ordinary%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Proton%20had%20said%20then%20in%20a%20statement.%20It%20also%20said%20this%20to%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20Indian%20IT%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20reported%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBlocking%20access%20to%20Proton%20is%20an%20ineffective%20and%20inappropriate%20response%20to%20the%20reported%20threats.%20It%20will%20not%20prevent%20cybercriminals%20from%20sending%20threats%20with%20another%20email%20service%20and%20will%20not%20be%20effective%20if%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20located%20outside%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Proton%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmails%20sent%20through%20Proton%20Mail%20are%20end-to-end%20encrypted%2C%20which%20means%20that%20no%20one%20except%20those%20communicating%20with%20each%20other%20using%20the%20service%20can%20read%20the%20messages%20they%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN1ZS1L1%2F%5C%22%3Epopular%20among%20some%20journalists%20and%20activists%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20focus%20on%20privacy%20and%20encryption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20website%2C%20Proton%20says%20the%20data%20of%20its%20email%20service%20users%20are%20%E2%80%9Cprotected%20by%20strict%20Swiss%20privacy%20laws%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Swiss%20law%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fproton.me%2Flegal%2Flaw-enforcement%5C%22%3EProton%20is%20also%20required%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccooperate%20with%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20on%20criminal%20investigations%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20Swiss%20laws%20and%20privacy%20regulations%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20can%20include%20transmitting%20data%20via%20Swiss%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProton%20also%20offers%20virtual%20private%20network%20%E2%80%93%20popularly%20known%20as%20VPN%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20password%20manager%20and%20cloud%20storage%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20reported%20decision%20comes%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20under%20Section%2069A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Funion-govt-uses-it-act-to-attack-press-freedom-asks-caravan-to-take-down-report%5C%22%3Easking%20it%20to%20take%20down%20an%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20covering%20allegations%20of%20torture%20and%20murder%20against%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magazine%20was%20told%20that%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20take%20down%20the%20article%20from%20its%20website%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20entire%20website%20would%20be%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20news%20website%C2%A0%3Cem%3EArticle14%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20recent%20report%20cited%20experts%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Ftakedown-of-hate-tracker-highlights-secrecy-around-modi-govt-s-internet-censorship-practices-65c59c3549d5a%5C%22%3Edodged%20procedural%20safeguards%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20passing%20orders%20to%20block%20online%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BThese%20procedural%20safeguards%20are%20enough%20if%20followed%20diligently%20%E2%80%A6%20But%20you%20will%20see%20in%20practice%20that%20they%20are%20indiscriminately%20abandoned%2C%E2%80%9D%20Radhika%20Roy%2C%20counsel%20at%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EArticle14%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707986987000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15135644%2FProton-Mail-logo.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fit-ministry-decides-to-block-proton-mail-after-fake-bomb-threats-in-tamil-nadu-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20officer%20representing%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20said%20during%20a%20content%20blocking%20committee%20meeting%20that%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%20behind%20fake%20bomb%20threats%20sent%20to%20schools%20using%20Proton%20Mail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fit-ministry-decides-to-block-proton-mail-after-fake-bomb-threats-in-tamil-nadu-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGreat%20Boon%20For%20Democracy%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20Poll%20Body%20Chief%20On%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20striking%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20boon%20for%20democracy%26quot%3B%2C%20former%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20SY%20Quraishi%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20top%20court%20bench%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%2C%20said%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20violates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20under%20the%20Constitution.%20It%20also%20ordered%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20disclose%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20the%20names%20of%20the%20contributors%20to%20the%20six-year-old%20scheme%20for%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20restore%20people's%20faith%20in%20democracy.%20This%20is%20the%20greatest%20thing%20that%20could%20have%20happened.%20This%20is%20the%20most%20historic%20judgement%20that%20we%20have%20got%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20last%20five-seven%20years.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20boon%20for%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Quraishi%20told%20PTI%20Videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20all%20concerned%20for%20the%20last%20so%20many%20years.%20Everyone%20who%20loves%20democracy%20was%20protesting%20about%20it.%20I%20myself%20wrote%20several%20articles%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20media%20many%20times.%20And%20every%20issue%20that%20we%20raised%20has%20been%20tackled%20in%20the%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20CEC%20also%20put%20out%20a%20post%20on%20X%20hailing%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElectoral%20Bonds%20declared%20unconstitutional%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Three%20cheers%20for%20the%20SC!%26quot%3B%20The%20scheme%2C%20which%20was%20notified%20by%20the%20government%20on%20January%202%2C%202018%2C%20was%20pitched%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20cash%20donations%20made%20to%20political%20parties%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuraishi%20said%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20donations%20happen%20through%20the%20banking%20system%20was%20fine%20but%20%26quot%3Bour%20contention%20was%20why%20should%20a%20donation%20given%20to%20a%20political%20party%20be%20kept%20a%20secret%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20donor%20wants%20secrecy%20but%20public%20wants%20transparency.%20Now%20why%20should%20the%20donor%20want%20secrecy%3F%20Because%20they%20want%20to%20hide%20the%20quid%20pro%20quo%2C%20the%20benefits%20they%20are%20getting%20in%20return%2C%20the%20licence%2C%20the%20contracts%20and%20even%20the%20bank%20loans%20with%20which%20they%20run%20away%20to%20the%20foreign%20lands.%20Is%20that%20why%20they%20they%20wanted%20secrecy%3F%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20government%20was%20trying%20to%20uphold%20the%20secrecy%20of%20donors...%20the%20same%20donors%20who%20have%20been%20donating%20for%20these%2070%20years.%20Suddenly%20there%20were%20in%20the%20need%20of%20secrecy.%20So%20that%20has%20now%20been%20done%20away%20with.%20I%20think%20it%20will%20make%20our%20democracy%20healthy%20once%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20best%20thing%20that%20could%20have%20happened%20to%20India's%20democracy%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20court%20has%20ordered%20that%20all%20the%20donations%20received%20in%20the%20last%20two-three%20years%20will%20be%20refunded%20and%20they%20will%20be%20disclosed%20to%20the%20nation...that%20will%20help%20us%20know%20whether%20there%20had%20been%20any%20quid%20pro%20quo%2C%20whether%20there%20had%20been%20any%20donor%20who%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20all%20kind%20of%20questionable%20pressure.%20A%20lot%20of%20things%20will%20come%20out%20from%20this%20judgement.%20In%20one%20word%2C%20it%20is%20a%20'historic'%20judgement%2C%26quot%3B%20Quraishi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%2C%20he%20said%20it%20will%20have%20impact%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20but%20not%20entirely%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20in%20any%20case%20political%20parties%20have%20been%20funded%20in%20the%20past.%20They%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20funded%20in%20the%20future.%20But%20this%20opaque%20method%20of%20funding%20has%20been%20removed%20and%20that%20is%20the%20best%20part%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20what%20he%20always%20demanded%20was%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20people%20donate%20to%20political%20parties.%20They%20have%20been%20donating%20for%2070%20years%2C%20there%20was%20no%20problem.%20There%20was%20no%20reprisal%20even%20if%20you%20donated%20to%20opposition%20parties.%20Nobody%20has%20taken%20any%20vindictive%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26