is%20the%20most%20high-profile%20former%20official%20to%20be%20charged%20with%20corruption%20since%20President%20Bola%20Tinubu%20took%20office%20in%20May.%20Although%20he%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20charges%20and%20is%20currently%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20authorities%20allege%20that%20Mr%20Emefiele%20unlawfully%20authorised%20the%20release%20of%20the%20money%20from%20the%20central%20bank%20vault%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20money%20was%20requested%20by%20the%20then%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20Federation%2C%20Boss%20Mustapha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Emefiele's%20alleged%20accomplices%20have%20been%20named%20as%20Adamu%20Abubakar%2C%20Imam%20Abubakar%20and%20Odoh%20Ocheme%2C%20a%20former%20central%20bank%20employee%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68282228%5C%22%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%2C%20citing%20the%20state-owned%20News%20Agency%20of%20Nigeria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20ordered%20their%20arrest%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20hours%20after%20Mr%20Mustapha%20testified%20in%20Mr%20Emefiele's%20trial.%20Mr%20Mustapha%20told%20the%20court%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Abuja%2C%20that%20neither%20he%20nor%20Mr%20Buhari%20had%20given%20their%20signature%20to%20approve%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20%246.2%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20signature%2C%20it%20is%20a%20faint%20attempt%20at%20reproducing%20%5Bformer%5D%20President%20Buhari's%20signature%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mustapha%20told%20the%20court.%20When%20shown%20the%20document%20used%20to%20withdraw%20the%20funds%2C%20Mr%20Mustapha%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20emanate%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20president%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdelta-flight-returns-to-amsterdam-after-maggots-fall-on-passengers-from-overhead-bin-5061175%5C%22%3EDelta%20Flight%20Returns%20To%20Amsterdam%