0confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20the%20power%20to%20issue%20such%20orders%20under%20the%20Rules%20and%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%20had%20not%20objected%20it.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana%20government%20issued%20orders%20to%20suspend%20internet%20services%20in%20that%20particular%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Fsuspension-of-telecom-services-internet-and-its-impact%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Esubmitted%20on%20December%202021%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20communications%20and%20information%20technology%20had%20observed%20that%20internet%20shutdowns%20have%20implications%20on%20national%20economy%2C%20freedom%20of%20press%2C%20education%20and%20healthcare%20services.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%20telecom%2Finternet%20shutdowns%20may%20be%20ordered%20on%20grounds%20of%20public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety.%20Public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety%20have%20not%20been%20defined%20in%20the%201885%20Act%20or%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Shashi%20Tharoor-led%20parliamentary%20committee%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20accounts%20on%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%20and%20Facebook%20which%20functioned%20as%20official%20pages%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20and%20unions%20ahead%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India%20seemingly%20upon%20government%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20p