rong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Section%20182%20of%20Companies%20Act%2C%202013%20governs%20an%20Indian%20company's%20right%20to%20contribute%20to%20a%20political%20party.%20Prior%20to%20the%20amendments%2C%20this%20was%20governed%20by%20a%20set%20of%20conditions%20-%20the%20donation%20should%20be%20authorised%20by%20the%20Board%3B%20(ii)%20the%20donation%20cannot%20be%20made%20in%20cash%2C%20(iii)%20the%20donation%20must%20be%20disclosed%20in%20the%20Company's%20profit%20and%20loss%20account%20(iv)%20the%20company%20cannot%20donate%20more%20than%207.5%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20average%20profits%20for%20three%20years%20and%20(v)%20the%20company%20must%20disclose%20the%20name%20of%20the%20party%20it%20had%20donated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202017%20amendments%20removed%20the%20cap%20on%20the%20amount%20a%20company%20can%20donate%20and%20also%20with%20the%20requirement%20of%20disclosing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20party%20it%20had%20donated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Government%20Argued%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20arguments%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20had%20argued%20that%20anonymity%20ensures%20that%20the%20donor%20does%20not%20face%20retribution%20or%20victimisation.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20donor%20wants%20is%20that%20the%20other%20party%20should%20not%20know.%20Suppose%2C%20as%20a%20contractor%2C%20I%20donate%20to%20the%20Congress%20Party.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20know%20because%20it%20might%20form%20a%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20earlier%20cap%20on%20donations%20did%20not%20work%20because%20shell%20companies%20were%20created%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20political%20donations.%20The%20scheme%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20aimed%20at%20disincentivising%20the%20creation%20of%20such%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20view%20to%20discourage%20creation%20of%20shell%20companies%2C%20we%20did%20this...%20If%20companies%20want%20to%20donate%20more%20than%207.5%25%20of%20their%20net%20profit%2C%20let%20the%20discretion%20remain%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20said%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20cap%2C%20companies%20would%20switch%20to%20cash%20donations%2C%20bringing%20black%20money%20into%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Court%20Said%20Today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20down%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20amendment%20to%20the%20Companies%20Act%20now%20becomes%20otiose%20-%20meaning%20redundant.%20A%20company%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20has%20graver%20influence%20on%20the%20political%20process%20than%20contributions%20by%20individuals.%20%26quot%3BContributions%20by%20companies%20are%20purely%20business%20transactions.%20Amendment%20to%20Section%20182%20Companies%20Act%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20for%20treating%20companies%20and%20individuals%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said%20that%20before%20the%20amendments%2C%20loss-making%20companies%20were%20not%20able%20to%20contribute.%20But%20the%20amendment%20potentially%20enabled%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangement%20between%20a%20company%20running%20into%20losses%20and%20a%20political%20party.%20%26quot%3BThe%20amendment%20does%20not%20recognise%20the%20harm%20of%20allowing%20loss-making%20companies%20to%20contribute%20due%20to%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20The%20amendment%20to%20Section%20182%20Companies%20Act%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20for%20not%20making%20a%20distinction%20between%20loss%20making%20and%20profit%20making%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20holding%20the%20amendments%20to%20Companies%20Act%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20disclosure%20requirements%20in%20Section%20182(3)%20were%20included%20to%20ensure%20that%20corporate%20interests%20do%20not%20have%20an%20undue%20influence%20in%20electoral%20democracy%2C%20and%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20electorate%20must%20be%20made%20aware%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20states.%C2%A0%26quot%3BUnlimited%20contribution%20by%20companies%20to%20political%20parties%20is%20antithetical%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20because%20it%20allows%20certain%20persons%2Fcompanies%20to%20wield%20their%20clout%20and%20resources%20to%20influence%20policy%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F6k6p2298_money-generic_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-how-supreme-court-verdict-undoes-big-change-5061700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Striking%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20also%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%20political%20funding%26quot%3B%20by%20corporates%20and%20said%20it%20violated%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-how-supreme-court-verdict-undoes-big-change-5061700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-how-supreme-court-verdict-undoes-big-change-5061700%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-how-supreme-court-verdict-undoes-big-change-5061700%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt's%20His%20Righ