d%20be%20part%20of%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June%2C%20Shah%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20talk%20about%20him%20%5Bsoon%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20confirmed%20that%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20would%20lead%20the%20'Men%20in%20Blues'%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20extraordinary%20T20%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20has%20the%20ability%2C%20we%20know.%20As%20he%20showed%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20where%20we%20won%2010%20matches%20in%20a%20row%20until%20the%20final.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20India%20will%20lift%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20under%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20captaincy%20in%20Barbados%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20last%20major%20trophy%20win%20was%20back%20in%202013%20when%20they%20beat%20England%20to%20win%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20the%20UK.%20Since%20then%2C%20India%20has%20shown%20incredible%20performances%20across%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cups%2C%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%2C%20but%20has%20fallen%20short%20every%20time%20of%20capturing%20the%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20will%20kick%20off%20on%20June%201%20and%20will%20be%20co-hosted%20by%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20the%20US.%20India%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20Group%20A%20alongside%20Ireland%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Canada%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Men%20in%20Blue%20will%20open%20their%20campaign%20against%20Ireland%20on%20June%205.%20Their%20second%20game%20of%20the%20tournament%20will%20be%20against%20arch-rival%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209.%20The%20final%20two%20games%20will%20be%20against%20Canada%20and%20USA%20on%20June%2012%20and%20June%2015%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20was%20on%20Wednesday%20renamed%20after%20veteran%20cricket%20administrator%20and%20former%20first-class%20cricketer%20Niranja