0Muslim%20teachers%2C%20students%20and%20parents%20not%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20event%2C%20exercising%20their%20right%20of%20religious%20independence%20as%20given%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Naeem%20Rabbani%2C%20member%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Muslim%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20issued%20in%20January%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Secondary%20Education%20Department%2C%20Bikaner%20had%20directed%20all%20district%20education%20officials%20to%20hold%20practice%20sessions%20of%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20during%20school%20prayers%20everyday%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20February%2015%20event.%20The%20order%20added%20that%20data%20pertaining%20to%20those%20who%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20event%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98world%20record%E2%80%99%20is%20also%20to%20be%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20had%20said%20that%20the%20participants%20will%20include%20students%2C%20teachers%2Fstaff%2C%20parents%20and%20local%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Rajasthan%20school%20education%20minister%20Madan%20Dilawar%20%E2%80%93%20a%20firebrand%20Hindutva%20face%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20had%20told%20reporters%20that%20all%20government%20schools%20will%20celebrate%20Surya%20Saptami%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20with%20attempts%20to%20make%20it%20the%20biggest%20such%20programme%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707978528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24151818%2F118281528_2076660359130829_177884413909856846_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Frajasthan-muslim-groups-urge-citizens-not-to-take-part-in-govt-schools-surya-namaskar-programmes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20Secondary%20Education%20Department%2C%20Bikaner%20last%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%