oundation%20started%20working%20to%20provide%20aid%20for%20surgical%20interventions%20for%20children%20born%20with%20congenital%20heart%20defects%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20leading%20hospitals%20in%20the%20country%2C%20under%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%20Program%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongenital%20Heart%20Disease%20(CHD)%20holds%20the%20foremost%20position%20globally%20in%20causing%20deaths%20linked%20to%20birth%20defects%2C%20persisting%20as%20a%20significant%20contributor%20to%20mortality%20and%20morbidity%20in%20both%20paediatric%20populations%20of%20developing%20and%20developed%20nations.%20In%20India%20only%2C%20it%20accounts%20for%2010%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%2C%20despite%20notable%20advancements%20in%20diagnosing%20and%20treating%20CHDs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Viresh%20Mahajan%2C%20Director%20of%20Paediatric%20Cardiac%20Sciences%20%26amp%3B%20Scientific%20Director%20of%20Clinical%20Research%2C%20Sarvodaya%20Hospital%2C%20Faridabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetecting%20congenital%20heart%20disease%20is%20possible%20during%20prenatal%20and%20postnatal%20stages%20through%20diverse%20diagnostic%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20sensitivity%20is%20critical%2C%20as%20any%20delay%20can%20prove%20fatal%20for%20infants.%20Timely%20treatment%20is%20very%20important%20as%20a%20child%20can%20lead%20a%20normal%20life%20in%20most%20congenital%20heart%20defects%20if%20treated%20at%20the%20optimal%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20state%20that%20early%20intervention%20is%20key.%20Dr%20Mahajan%20adds%20that%20children%20with%20CHD%20can%20lead%20healthy%20and%20lengthy%20lives%20with%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-17