20how%20do%20we%20cultivate%20these%3F%20We%20realised%20that%20we%20have%20to%20start%20from%20scratch%2C%20make%20our%20own%20spawn%20to%20make%20extracts%20and%20eventually%20the%20wellness%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Jashid%20undertook%20training%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Horticulture%20Research%20(IIHR)%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20cultivating%20mushrooms.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20the%20couple%20officially%20launched%20their%20company%20Nuvedo%20in%202021%20by%20exhausting%20their%20collective%20savings%20of%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20DIY%20kit%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20couple%20started%20researching%20the%20field%2C%20they%20found%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20the%20cultivation%20of%20mushrooms.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20misconceptions%20surrounding%20mushrooms%20because%20they%20are%20seen%20growing%20in%20agricultural%20waste%20and%20unhygienic%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prithvi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20essential%20for%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20solution%20that%20allowed%20people%20to%20be%20educated%20on%20mushroom%20cultivation.%20Their%20quest%20led%20them%20to%20design%20a%20DIY%20mushroom%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1oCwSyLWhT%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1oCwSyLWhT%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E