10%20days%2C%20you%20will%20get%20your%20first%20harvest%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20this%2C%20you%20can%20harvest%20a%20total%20of%20500%20grams%20of%20mushroom%20in%20two%20to%20three%20harvests%20from%20one%20kit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20completely%20sustainable%20as%20they%20grow%20on%20agricultural%20waste.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20sunlight%20and%20anybody%20can%20grow%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNuvedo-1707484707.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20of%20Nuvedo%20startup%20that%20is%20based%20out%20of%20Bengaluru.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNuvedo-1707484707.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNuvedo-1707484707-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNuvedo-1707484707-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNuvedo-1707484707-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNuvedo-1707484707-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341355%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20of%20Bengaluru-based%20Nuvedo%20startup.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Nithin%20George%20bought%20their%20pink%20oyster%20grow%20kit%20and%20says%20that%20he%20continues%20to%20be%20fascinated%20